{"tid":1939860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流浮山有無刀手我真係唔知，將軍澳出口罩一定快過流浮山先","createTime":"2020-03-23T11:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T19:44:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a03b90b4bad57297f0e58a4fd607e1a7ded960","tid":1939860,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hktvmall/posts/2691186007653937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhktvmall%2Fposts%2F2691186007653937&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=3decb3dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hktvmall/posts/2691186007653937</a><br />\n<br />\n㊙【先睹為快🔥口罩機開箱】🔥<br />\n<br />\n來自美國及台灣防菌Filter？Ready✅<br />\n有認證無塵車間？Ready✅<br />\n口罩機？Ready✅‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<br />\n皇天不負有心人😘等咗足足一月，口罩機終於由台灣送到嚟將軍澳總部！（R小隊鬆一口氣💨）聽到口罩機到埗開始組裝，小編差啲連個心💓都跳埋出嚟，裝完之後仲要做一啲調整及試產&hellip; 唔好講咁多，去片！<br />\n<br />\n雖然等港產口罩等到花兒也謝了🥀不過唔使咁快攞銀包，因為口罩一定要做足功夫，質素同可靠嘅生產設備最緊要，否則戴咗等於無戴！所以必須要做到防菌防病毒🦠嘅合規格口罩😷<br />\n<br />\n<strong>當口罩機準備投入生產之前，無塵車間會再做一次大清潔同消毒 (之後小編就唔入得去clean room啦拜拜~) 之後仲要通過測試同驗證，喺兩至三星期之後口罩就可以開賣俾大家帶返屋企。小編會監察R小隊嘅工作進展，大家要等我哋啊！</strong><br />\n<br />\n疫情不定，大家記住減少社交活動、勤洗手，保持身體健康💪🏻～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/90276703_2691184504320754_1537867049546547200_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=5DCFeNZzJtsAX9sYMNb&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=b26921ac1cd67ab2e7b145496c1eff49&amp;oe=5E9DC21A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F90276703_2691184504320754_1537867049546547200_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D5DCFeNZzJtsAX9sYMNb%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3Db26921ac1cd67ab2e7b145496c1eff49%26oe%3D5E9DC21A&h=e5f5a14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/90718268_2691185957653942_4009951174588366848_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=ZaLgxH4zB3MAX-ECtLe&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=74ed67074b79668c4950e1289085b9de&amp;oe=5E9F5177\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F90718268_2691185957653942_4009951174588366848_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DZaLgxH4zB3MAX-ECtLe%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D74ed67074b79668c4950e1289085b9de%26oe%3D5E9F5177&h=6be40924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/90143889_2691184497654088_87876040193474560_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=yW9Te9rxfT8AX8HAjxM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=aeadf3fb7b8e48ce000428a3df0ae396&amp;oe=5E9E9999\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F90143889_2691184497654088_87876040193474560_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DyW9Te9rxfT8AX8HAjxM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Daeadf3fb7b8e48ce000428a3df0ae396%26oe%3D5E9E9999&h=b303b062&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8bbaee350dd64eae252303dc48949c40d671959","tid":1939860,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a1c3b37b66f5fae82a158eb90c3d7316460f39","tid":1939860,"uid":163943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88021e18406b6055011d1d76bb13dd3824c94d1f","tid":1939860,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T11:41:2